          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1451.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once browned, add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>flour </strong>and cook for 1 min, stirring until combined</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>beef</strong> <strong>stock cube<span class=\"text-danger text-highlight\">[s]</span></strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> and <strong>shredded kale </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 8-10 min or until thickened – this is your <strong>beef mixture</strong></p>\n<p>Meanwhile, grate the<strong> cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
